  {"id":"w15_01","english":"Although sea turtles can stay underwater for some time, they must come up to the surface to breathe from time to time.","chinese":"虽然海龟可以在水下待一段时间，但它们必须时不时浮出水面呼吸。","week":15,"theme":"nature","type":"sentence"},
